snippet.title: YO-KAI WATCH Wibble Wobble Launch Trailer | Play Meow
snippet.description:
Jibanyan, Komasan, and other favorite Yo-kai have turned into wibbly wobbly, bite-sized Wib Wob! Level up individual Yo-kai, explore the world of Springdale, and defeat Yo-kai to befriend them.

A joint production between LEVEL-5 and NHN PlayArt, YO-KAI WATCH Wibble Wobble is an intense yet extremely cute mix of puzzle and RPG mechanics.

YO-KAI WATCH Wibble Wobble is now available for download in the U.S., Canada, and Australia. The game is free to download and play, and includes in-app purchases.

Google Play
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Level5.YWWWUS&hl=en

App Store
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id1085461253?mt=8
